column5: My buddy Tyler and I took a quick trip for Steelhead back in May, timing the run is so unpredictable and we were abit late but still managed some fish, this is how our first day went
That's some sweet scenery, I'm glad you got into them.  You guys stayed up there for 3 days?
Gonna watch this tonight.  I always enjoy your content.
Thanks for sharing, some beautiful scenery up there.
Lots of bush wacking, lots of beautiful river and your scenery coverage was sweet. That was one great video.  Enjoyed very much.
Thanks guys it was a great trip, couple more days of it to come   That's some sweet scenery, I'm glad you got into them.  You guys stayed up there for 3 days?  Yup it was a 3 day trip
